你去哪  小伙子?
Where you going, boyo?

1141
02:01:07,830 --> 02:01:09,230
跟我来
Come along.

1142
02:01:09,430 --> 02:01:11,130
跟我来
Come on.

1143
02:01:13,730 --> 02:01:16,530
告诉我们  你惹了什么麻烦?
Tell us, John, what's the trouble?

1144
02:01:17,530 --> 02:01:19,230
没麻烦  比尔
No trouble, Bill.

1145
02:01:22,330 --> 02:01:24,830
还在为你的那些朋友保密?
Still hiding out with your friends?

1146
02:01:28,030 --> 02:01:32,530
不是  我和他们不是一路的  比尔
No, I'm... I'm not with them, Bill.

1147
02:01:32,930 --> 02:01:35,930
我和你是一路的  和本地帮是一路的
I'm with you. I'm with the Natives.

1148
02:01:40,530 --> 02:01:44,630
据我所知  你一直都是本地帮的...
You always was a Native as far as I'm interested, John...

1149
02:01:47,230 --> 02:01:50,030
...直到你成为叛徒之前
...till you became a stag.

1150
02:01:53,430 --> 02:01:57,030
你说你是本地帮的  你知道本地帮的人是什么样的吗?
You tell me you're a Native. Do you want to know what a Native is?

1151
02:01:59,030 --> 02:02:02,430
本地帮的好汉
A Native is a man...

1152
02:02:02,630 --> 02:02:07,230
...为了国家不惜流血牺牲
...what's willing to give his life for his country...

1153
02:02:09,330 --> 02:02:11,530
...就象我父亲那样
...like my father done.

1154
02:02:14,730 --> 02:02:18,530
你愿意这么做吗?小朋友?
Are you willing to do that, my young friend?

1155
02:02:27,730 --> 02:02:30,830
约翰  约翰尼!
John. Johnny!

1156
02:02:38,430 --> 02:02:40,330
约翰尼?
Johnny?

1157
02:02:49,830 --> 02:02:51,730
约翰
John...

1158
02:03:04,030 --> 02:03:06,730
我伤得很重
It hurts too much.

1159
02:03:12,930 --> 02:03:15,030
杀了我吧
Just kill me.

1160
02:03:19,730 --> 02:03:22,030
杀了我吧
Just kill me.

1161
02:03:23,630 --> 02:03:26,830
求你了  求你了
Please, please.

1162
02:03:34,530 --> 02:03:36,430
求你了
Please.

1163
02:03:38,830 --> 02:03:40,630
求你了
Please.

1164
02:03:44,830 --> 02:03:47,230
对不起  约翰尼
I'm sorry, Johnny.

1165
02:04:02,830 --> 02:04:05,130
天主圣母玛利亚
Holy Mary, mother of God, pray for us sinners...

1166
02:04:05,430 --> 02:04:08,730
求您现在和在我们临终时为我们罪人祈求天主  阿门
...now and at the hour of our death. Amen.

1167
02:04:09,530 --> 02:04:11,730
安息吧  妈妈
Rest in peace, Ma.

1168
02:04:14,630 --> 02:04:16,930
你在这里做什么?
What are you doing here, boyo?

1169
02:04:23,330 --> 02:04:26,530
这黑鬼上教堂干什么?
What's a nigger doing in this church?

1170
02:04:30,930 --> 02:04:33,030
死兔帮应该怎么对付本地帮?
What's a Dead Rabbit doing with the Natives?

1171
02:04:33,330 --> 02:04:36,330
本地帮没有黑鬼  本地帮和死兔帮信仰相同
There's no niggers in the Natives. Natives and Rabbits is one thing.

1172
02:04:36,630 --> 02:04:38,530
可是黑鬼跑到教堂里来却是另一码事
A nigger in the church is something else!

1173
02:04:38,830 --> 02:04:40,630
你投靠了本地帮你去为本地帮祈祷吧
You run with the Natives, pray with them!

1174
02:04:40,930 --> 02:04:43,830
你们会象你们的人一样被穿在桩子上
You're gonna wind up on a stake like your man did!

1175
02:04:44,830 --> 02:04:46,030
麦格罗恩
McGloin.

1176
02:04:46,230 --> 02:04:50,430
神父  天啊  你知道有个黑鬼跑到你的教堂里来了吗?
Father! Jesus, did you know there's a nigger in your church?

1177
02:05:08,730 --> 02:05:11,130
天啊
Jesus.

1178
02:05:33,730 --> 02:05:36,130
天翻地覆了
The earth turns...

1179
02:05:37,030 --> 02:05:39,630
...可我们并未觉察到
...but we don 't feel it move.

1180
02:05:42,330 --> 02:05:45,030
直到某天晚上才突然发现
Then one night you look up.

1181
02:05:46,230 --> 02:05:51,130
星星之火  终于燎原
One spark, and the sky is on fire.

1182
02:06:02,630 --> 02:06:05,430
真是令人激动的场面
It's a touching spectacle.

1183
02:06:07,330 --> 02:06:10,230
你们准备好了我们会回来的
We'll come back when you're ready for us.

1184
02:06:16,630 --> 02:06:20,230
过去就是我们的指路明灯
The past is the torch that lights our way.

1185
02:06:20,730 --> 02:06:25,930
先辈们已经指引了我们该走的路  我们应该大步前行
Where our fathers have shown us the path, we shall follow.

1186
02:06:27,930 --> 02:06:32,130
我们的信仰是敌人最惧怕的武器
Our faith is the weapon most feared by our enemies.

1187
02:06:32,530 --> 02:06:37,230
凭藉信仰我们可以发动同胞对抗欲置我们于死地的敌人
For thereby shall we lift our people up against those who would destroy us.

1188
02:06:37,630 --> 02:06:42,330
我们称自己为'死兔帮'  为了牢记我们过去经受的苦难
Our name is called the Dead Rabbits to remind all of our suffering...

1189
02:06:42,730 --> 02:06:46,430
为了团结正在经受苦难的人们
...and as a call to those who suffer still to join our ranks...

1190
02:06:46,830 --> 02:06:51,430
...团结那些从我们共同的家乡  漂洋过海  不远万里来到此地的人们
...however so far they may have strayed from our common home across the sea.

1191
02:06:51,730 --> 02:06:59,230
因为众人同心  其利断金
For with great numbers must come great strength...and the salvation of our people.

1192
02:06:59,830 --> 02:07:02,130
-你们那些事我们不想掺乎进来  -有多少人住在这里?
-We don't want your business. -How many men live here?

1193
02:07:02,330 --> 02:07:04,830
-都得来登记  -你们不能强迫我入伍
-You have to register. -You can't force me to join.

1194
02:07:05,030 --> 02:07:06,630
-你有300美元吗?  -当然没有
-Have you got $300? - Of course not.

1195
02:07:06,930 --> 02:07:10,230
哪他妈的去搞300美元?  如果你被征召  想要免服兵役
-Who's got $300? -Lf you're drafted, release from service...

1196
02:07:10,530 --> 02:07:13,830
需要缴纳300美元才行  这是征兵法规定的
...can only be secured for $300, according to the Conscription Act.

1197
02:07:14,130 --> 02:07:16,630
-否则  你就得入伍  -谁他妈有300美元?
-Otherwise, you have to serve! -Who the hell's got $300?

1198
02:07:16,930 --> 02:07:20,430
你必须应征    除非你有300美元
You have to serve, sir, unless you have $300!

1199
02:07:20,830 --> 02:07:22,730
-伙计们  -从哪来滚回哪去
-Boys! - Go back to where you came from!

1200
02:07:22,930 --> 02:07:27,130
我在此土生土长  你是移民到此你就必须为这个国家战斗
I'm born in this country. You immigrated here. You will fight for this country!

1201
02:07:27,430 --> 02:07:29,930
天啊  战争真是可怕的灾难
Sweet Jesus! War does terrible things to men.

1202
02:07:30,330 --> 02:07:36,130
-滚回富人区去  -300美元?  -又一场富人的战争
-Get back uptown where you belong! -$300? So it's another rich man's war.

1203
02:07:36,430 --> 02:07:39,430
先生  我想和此人谈谈
Sir, I request an audience with this man.

1204
02:07:41,630 --> 02:07:43,630
纽约已经没人说英语了吗?
No one speak English in New York anymore?

1205
02:07:43,930 --> 02:07:46,030
-我不懂你说什么  -原来你会说英语
-Don't understand. -You do speak English.

1206
02:07:48,030 --> 02:07:52,230
爱华亭小姐能否别把枪口这么对着我?
I wonder if Miss Everdeane could angle her rifle in some other direction.

1207
02:07:57,830 --> 02:08:02,330
瓦伦先生  不知道你是否明白这份宣传的真正价值
I wonder, Mr. Vallon, if you understand the true value of this sort of publicity.

1208
02:08:06,430 --> 02:08:10,230
大教主本人与五点区的半数爱尔兰人立场一致
The archbishop himself, shoulder to shoulder with the Irish in the Five Points.

1209
02:08:10,930 --> 02:08:13,930
我愿意与你们结盟对抗比尔.卡丁...
I'm offering to form an alliance with you against Bill Cutting...

1210
02:08:14,330 --> 02:08:16,930
...及他支持的持本土论观点的候选人
...and his slate of Nativist candidates.

1211
02:08:17,230 --> 02:08:21,030
我愿意出个很好的价钱给每位投票给坦慕尼的爱尔兰人
I'll negotiate a handsome fee for every Irish vote you send Tammany's way...

1212
02:08:21,430 --> 02:08:23,630
在接下来的选举中
...in the coming elections.

1213
02:08:25,130 --> 02:08:28,130
我需要在五点区物色一位新盟友
I need a new friend in the Five Points, son.

1214
02:08:31,430 --> 02:08:33,730
我希望这位朋友是你
I'd like that friend to be you.

1215
02:08:37,030 --> 02:08:39,630
等一下  特威德先生
Now, just a moment, Mr. Tweed.

1216
02:08:39,930 --> 02:08:42,930
如果你能拿到你希望的选票
Suppose we do get you those votes.

1217
02:08:45,430 --> 02:08:47,530
你能不能支持我选择的一位爱尔兰候选人?
Would you back an Irish candidate of my choosing?

1218
02:08:47,830 --> 02:08:50,730
-恐怕不行  -如果所有爱尔兰人都投你的票呢?
-I don't think so. -What if we get you all the Irish votes?

1219
02:08:51,230 --> 02:08:54,730
瓦伦先生  这简直是天方夜谭
That will only happen in the reign of Queen Dick.

1220
02:08:56,830 --> 02:08:59,030
-你说什么?  -就是永远不可能发生的事
-Beg your pardon? -It will never happen.

1221
02:08:59,230 --> 02:09:02,530
我倒是可以支持爱尔兰人竞选市议员
I might be persuaded to back an Irish candidate for, say, alderman.

1222
02:09:02,930 --> 02:09:05,630
-市议员?  爱尔兰人已经有了市议员了
-Alderman? -We've already got Irish aldermen.

1223
02:09:05,830 --> 02:09:09,130
-正因为如此  -所以 比市议员大的是什么?
-So we have. That's why... -Well, what's bigger than alderman?

1224
02:09:10,730 --> 02:09:14,330
治安官  治安官  好了  特威德先生
Sheriff. Sheriff. All right, Mr. Tweed.

1225
02:09:14,630 --> 02:09:18,430
你支持一位爱尔兰人竞选纽约市或县的治安官
You back an Irishman for sheriff of the city and county of New York...

1226
02:09:18,730 --> 02:09:20,130
...我们会让他当选
...and we'll get him elected.

1227
02:09:20,330 --> 02:09:23,530
我爱你们爱尔兰人  孩子  可高于市议员的职位你们永远不可能得到
I love the Irish, but higher than alderman you shall never climb.

1228
02:09:23,830 --> 02:09:26,230
-为什么呢?  -首先  没一个人
-Well, why not? -For one thing, no man living...

1229
02:09:26,530 --> 02:09:28,230
...能决定所有爱尔兰人的投票方向  -我能
...can consolidate the Irish vote. - I can.

1230
02:09:28,530 --> 02:09:30,630
其次  此话不怀恶意
And for another, I mean no effrontery...

1231
02:09:30,830 --> 02:09:34,930
...找不出一位爱尔兰人适合竞选治安官
...no one's yet found an Irish candidate for sheriff worth voting for.

1232
02:09:37,530 --> 02:09:38,830
蒙克
Monk.

1233
02:09:39,930 --> 02:09:41,230
请看
Here.

1234
02:09:45,730 --> 02:09:48,330
看起来象我祖父一样镇定从容
He's to have me looking as sober as me own grandfather.

1235
02:09:48,530 --> 02:09:52,530
-他肯定很了不起  -他是个烂酒鬼
-Another great man, I'm sure. -A thorough drunken bastard.

1236
02:09:54,830 --> 02:09:56,530
我愿意试一试
Could I say what I want?

1237
02:09:57,730 --> 02:09:59,930
正是我想要的
Well, that's why I wanted you.

1238
02:10:00,230 --> 02:10:03,030
我们选的代表们是一伙盗匪
Our elected representatives are a gang of thieves...

1239
02:10:03,330 --> 02:10:04,930
...赌咒发誓要为我们谋取更好的权益的同时
...who swear to better our lot...

1240
02:10:05,230 --> 02:10:08,030
...手却伸到我们的腰包里去了
...while dipping their hands deep into our pockets.

1241
02:10:08,230 --> 02:10:11,830
我与社区领袖们并肩作战比如这位比尔.卡丁先生
I stand shoulder to shoulder with community leaders like Bill Cutting...

1242
02:10:12,430 --> 02:10:16,130
对抗所有敢于侵害民主的人
...against any and all inroads into our fine democracy.

1243
02:10:16,530 --> 02:10:20,530
我要确保没人能夺走你们千辛万苦得来的东西
I'll see to it that no one takes away what you've earned by pluck and application.

1244
02:10:20,930 --> 02:10:22,830
-入侵的爱尔兰蛮子
-To invading hordes of Hibernians!

1245
02:10:23,030 --> 02:10:26,930
去把票投给沃尔特麦克金
You go to the polls and you put your mark next to the name Walter McGinn.

1246
02:10:27,330 --> 02:10:31,730
-打倒那帮吃土豆的人比如那边那堆人  他们抢走了我们的饭碗
-Against the potato eaters, like them over there, thieving our jobs!

1247
02:10:32,130 --> 02:10:34,430
为什么这么多爱尔兰人要到南方去送死?
Why should so many Irish die down south...

1248
02:10:34,630 --> 02:10:39,130
...我们的战场不是在南方各州  而是在这里的大街小巷里
...when the first war to win is not down in Dixie, but right here in these streets?

1249
02:10:41,130 --> 02:10:43,830
谁是五点区最好的斗士?
And who's the finest street fighter in the Five Points?

1250
02:10:44,130 --> 02:10:46,230
-蒙克  -没错
-Monk! - That's right.

1251
02:10:46,530 --> 02:10:49,130
那么让全城都听到你们的声音
Now, let the whole damn city hear it!

1252
02:10:50,730 --> 02:10:52,430
这人天生就是干这个的
That man was right born for this.

1253
02:10:52,730 --> 02:10:55,630
他杀过44人  打败的更有百人之多
Well, he's killed 44 men, laid low a couple hundred more.

1254
02:10:55,930 --> 02:10:57,430
-是真的吗?  -真的
-Is that right? -That's right.

1255
02:10:57,730 --> 02:10:59,730
我应该让他竞选市长
I should have run him for mayor.

1256
02:11:01,930 --> 02:11:05,130
好了  把他们全带走  今天是选举日
All right, line them up. It's election day!

1257
02:11:05,830 --> 02:11:09,030
快点  你这畜生
Not so fast, you little yellow bastard!

1258
02:11:09,330 --> 02:11:11,030
起来
Come on!

1259
02:11:14,930 --> 02:11:16,830
起来  畜生  给我投票去
Come on, you bastard, we need your vote.

1260
02:11:17,130 --> 02:11:20,430
畜生?我过去为你们而战  黑鬼
Bastard? I fought for you, nigger. I lost an arm for you.

1261
02:11:20,630 --> 02:11:22,430
还没算完  马上跟我走
Well, that's a start. Now, come on.

1262
02:11:22,630 --> 02:11:24,330
太阳出来了  太阳出来了
Rise and shine. Rise and shine.

1263
02:11:24,630 --> 02:11:27,630
我们这个伟大的国家里牛鬼蛇神也能投票
In this great country of ours, even the hop fiends get to vote!

1264
02:11:29,030 --> 02:11:30,730
别打扮了  加快动作
Less art and more haste, Don.

1265
02:11:31,030 --> 02:11:33,430
-你去哪?  -我今天已经投了票
-Where are you going? - I already voted today.

1266
02:11:33,630 --> 02:11:36,530
投给了蒙克和坦慕尼  各两次
Cast for Monk and Tammany, by God. Twice.

1267
02:11:36,930 --> 02:11:40,630
两次?  才两次?  你就是这样行使公民权利的吗?  跟我来
Twice? Only twice? You call that doing your civic duty? Come with me.

1268
02:11:40,830 --> 02:11:43,330
你别走  回来坐下
Oh, no, you don't. Get back and sit down.

1269
02:11:43,630 --> 02:11:45,630
又一个  好好给他清理一下
Here's another one. Clean him up good.

1270
02:11:45,930 --> 02:11:48,430
把他们的胡子剃了  让他们再去投一次
Shave their beards and send them back to vote again.

1271
02:11:48,830 --> 02:11:51,530
好的  伙计们  投蒙克和坦慕尼  蒙克和坦慕尼
All right, boys. Vote Monk, Tammany. Monk, Tammany!

1272
02:11:51,830 --> 02:11:54,830
先生们  我们伟大的城市需要一座新法院
So, gentlemen, what our great city needs is a new courthouse.

1273
02:11:55,030 --> 02:11:57,830
我希望未来的法院应该比较经济节约
I propose it should be a modest, economical structure.

1274
02:11:58,030 --> 02:11:59,830
失陪一会  什么事?
Excuse me one moment.

1275
02:12:00,030 --> 02:12:03,430
蒙克已经比其他对手领先3000多票了
Monk's already won by 3000 more votes than there are voters.

1276
02:12:03,830 --> 02:12:07,230
这么少?  设法提高到2、3万去  我们不要小胜  我们要大捷
Three? Make it 20, 30. We don't need a victory. We need a Roman triumph!

1277
02:12:07,430 --> 02:12:11,530
-我们没有多余的选票了  -记住从政的首要准则
-But we don't have any more ballots. -Remember the first rule of politics:

1278
02:12:11,930 --> 02:12:15,130
选票不代表最后结果  最后的计票才代表结果  是计票
The ballots don't make the results, the counters make the results.

1279
02:12:15,430 --> 02:12:16,430
继续计吧
Keep counting.

1280
02:12:48,430 --> 02:12:50,330
比尔送来的
It's from Bill.

1281
02:12:53,830 --> 02:12:55,330
蒙克
Monk.

1282
02:13:15,230 --> 02:13:18,030
五点区的公民们...
Citizens of the Five Points...

1283
02:13:18,630 --> 02:13:22,430
比尔.卡丁先生试图挑起纷争
...Mr. Bill Cutting is attempting to draw me into an argument...

1284
02:13:22,730 --> 02:13:27,130
最终无疑会引发流血事件进而危及我的办公室的安全
...that would no doubt end in bloodshed and the compromising of my office.

1285
02:13:28,030 --> 02:13:29,930
大家什么看法?
What do you think?

1286
02:13:30,830 --> 02:13:34,430
我该选择按老规矩一言不发地应战
Should I engage in silence this relic of the ancient law?

1287
02:13:34,730 --> 02:13:40,930
还是选择在新的形势下  新的环境里作你们的代言人?
Or shall I be your chosen voice in a new testament, in the new world?

1288
02:13:47,130 --> 02:13:48,830
你看到了  比尔
There you are, Bill.

1289
02:13:50,530 --> 02:13:52,430
人们的态度已经表明了
The people have spoken.

1290
02:13:54,030 --> 02:13:58,030
长期的暴力纷争已经让人麻木了
The very notion of violent reprisal benumbs them.

1291
02:14:00,330 --> 02:14:01,930
上来吧
Come on up.

1292
02:14:02,530 --> 02:14:05,830
看我们能否以民主的方式解决纷争
Let's see if we can resolve our grievances the democratic way.

1293
02:14:29,230 --> 02:14:33,830
朋友  这是少数派的投票
That, my friends, is the minority vote.

1294
02:14:35,130 --> 02:14:39,030
知道我的厉害了吧  滋味如何?
Now you've tasted my mutton. How do you like it?

1295
02:14:39,330 --> 02:14:40,630
看着
Look.

1296
02:14:40,930 --> 02:14:43,330
我让你看看这里
I want you to see this.

1297
02:14:46,230 --> 02:14:48,330
这就是你  就在这
This is you. Right here.

1298
02:14:48,530 --> 02:14:52,230
第45条  你这个爱尔兰狗杂种
Notch 45, you Irish bog bastard.

1299
02:15:03,930 --> 02:15:07,330
你们把他烧了吧看看他的骨灰会不会变成绿色
Why don't you burn him, see if his ashes turn green.

1300
02:15:12,730 --> 02:15:15,030
'命运眷顾勇者'
Fortune favors the bold!

1301
02:15:27,530 --> 02:15:31,430
-你杀了选举出来的官员?  -谁选了他?
-You killed an elected official? -Who elected him?

1302
02:15:31,830 --> 02:15:34,830
你不知道你干了些什么
You don't know what you've done to yourself.

1303
02:15:40,530 --> 02:15:42,930
我知道你的作风
I know your works.

1304
02:15:43,630 --> 02:15:45,730
你不冷也不热
You are neither cold nor hot.

1305
02:15:46,030 --> 02:15:50,130
因为你就是个冷血动物  我要呸在你身上
So because you are lukewarm, I will spew you out of my mouth.

1306
02:15:51,830 --> 02:15:54,230
你自己营造你的肮脏世界去吧
You can build your filthy world without me.

1307
02:15:54,530 --> 02:15:56,930
我干掉了父亲我还会干掉儿子
I took the father. Now I'll take the son.

1308
02:15:57,130 --> 02:16:01,830
你告诉小瓦伦我要用他的血油漆天堂广场
You tell young Vallon I'm gonna paint Paradise Square with his blood.

1309
02:16:02,430 --> 02:16:03,930
刷两层
Two coats.

1310
02:16:04,530 --> 02:16:07,030
我要用他的内脏装点我的卧室
I'll festoon my bedchamber with his guts.

1311
02:16:07,430 --> 02:16:09,730
至于你  操蛋坦慕尼.霍尔先生
As for you, Mr. Tammany-fucking-Hall...

1312
02:16:10,030 --> 02:16:11,830
如果胆敢再踏入五点区
...you come down to the Points again...

1313
02:16:12,030 --> 02:16:15,430
...我就会亲手宰了你
...and you'll be dispatched by mine own hand.

1314
02:16:17,430 --> 02:16:22,530
回去参加你的庆典让我好好吃饭  老子给了你不少了
Now get back to your celebration and let me eat in peace. I paid you fair.

1315
02:16:46,630 --> 02:16:48,230
停
Stop.

1316
02:16:49,330 --> 02:16:50,830
起
Raise.

1317
02:17:33,930 --> 02:17:36,130
狗娘养的
You son of a bitch!

1318
02:17:40,130 --> 02:17:42,030
挑战
Challenge.

1319
02:17:43,430 --> 02:17:45,730
接受
Challenge accepted.

1320
02:18:37,430 --> 02:18:40,730
终于来了  征兵的第一天
And then it came, the first day of the draft.

1321
02:18:41,130 --> 02:18:46,230
托马斯.内尔  安德鲁.路易斯  约瑟夫.弗林
Thomas O'Neill. Andrew Lewis. Joseph flynn.

1322
02:18:46,630 --> 02:18:49,730
他们念着被征召人的名字仿佛他们已经死了一样
They read out the draftees ' names like they was dead already.

1323
02:18:49,930 --> 02:18:54,130
安德鲁.马丁  J.B.克里森
Andrew Martin. J.B. Gleason.

1324
02:18:54,530 --> 02:18:57,130
-奥康尔卫士帮  -搅屎棍帮
-The O'Connell Guard. -The Plug Uglies.

1325
02:18:57,430 --> 02:19:00,530
-我们这边  各帮派聚集在一起  -四十大盗帮
-As for us, the tribes were gathered. -Forty Thieves.

1326
02:19:01,030 --> 02:19:03,430
-齐切斯特帮  -战鼓擂响
-The Chichesters. -The drums was beating.

1327
02:19:03,730 --> 02:19:04,930
死兔帮
The Dead Rabbits.

1328
02:19:05,130 --> 02:19:07,930
-美国卫士帮  -亚特兰蒂帮
-The American Guard. -The Atlantic Guard.

1329
02:19:08,330 --> 02:19:10,930
-屠夫帮  -鲍瑞小子
-The Slaughter Housers. -The Bowery Boys.

1330
02:19:11,130 --> 02:19:13,330
美洲本地人联帮
The Confederation of American Natives.

1331
02:19:14,830 --> 02:19:15,930
詹姆斯.穆尼
James Mooney.

1332
02:19:16,230 --> 02:19:19,530
可我们只看到一只手挡在我们面前
But all we could see was the hand in front of us.

1333
02:19:19,830 --> 02:19:21,730
肖恩.奥康耐尔
Sean O'Connell.

1334
02:19:22,030 --> 02:19:26,030
G.W.莫里斯  约翰.多洛
G.W. Morris. John Doyle.

1335
02:19:26,330 --> 02:19:28,930
-时间?  -你挑
-When? -Whenever you like.

1336
02:19:29,130 --> 02:19:31,330
-明日黎明时分  -地点?
-Daybreak tomorrow. -Ground?

1337
02:19:31,530 --> 02:19:33,630
天堂广场
Paradise Square.

1338
02:19:33,830 --> 02:19:35,530
武器?
Weapons?

1339
02:19:35,830 --> 02:19:40,830
-你来决定吧  -砖  棒  斧  刀
-That I leave up to you. -Bricks, bats, axes, knives...

1340
02:19:41,430 --> 02:19:42,830
手枪?
Pistols?

1341
02:19:44,430 --> 02:19:45,830
不用手枪
No pistols.

1342
02:19:47,030 --> 02:19:49,030
好孩子
Good boy.

1343
02:19:51,530 --> 02:19:54,430
条件已谈好  会议结束
The terms are resolved. The council's concluded.

1344
02:19:56,630 --> 02:20:00,530
汤马斯.麦克维
Thomas McEvoy. W.H. Miles.

1345
02:20:00,730 --> 02:20:03,730
-该死的征兵见鬼去吧  -送他们下地狱
-To hell with your damned draft! -Give them hellfire, boys!

1346
02:20:04,030 --> 02:20:05,530
撕了他们
Rip them apart!

1347
02:20:12,630 --> 02:20:15,030
杀死有钱的王八蛋
Kill the rich bastards!

1348
02:20:21,430 --> 02:20:22,930
富人区
Uptown!

1349
02:20:24,630 --> 02:20:26,330
你们不能把我的儿子带走
You're not getting my son!

1350
02:20:31,930 --> 02:20:34,530
在富人区征兵处...
Uptown at the draft office...

1351
02:20:34,730 --> 02:20:39,630
...警察打破了几个人的脑袋众人四处逃散
...the cops broke a few skulls, and everybody run away.

1352
02:20:40,830 --> 02:20:43,130
谣言四起
But the word was spreading...

1353
02:20:43,430 --> 02:20:45,230
危机四伏
...and the dark.

1354
02:20:46,430 --> 02:20:47,730
而在第五街
Up on Fifth Avenue...

1355
02:20:48,030 --> 02:20:51,230
...斯盖马洪家族和他的手下倒是神定气闲
...the Schermerhorns and their mob breathed a little easy.

1356
02:20:51,530 --> 02:20:54,330
不过是发泄一下反对征兵的情绪
Just a brief burst of anger over Mr. Lincoln's draft.

1357
02:20:54,630 --> 02:20:56,730
我认为不是什么大问题
Entirely justifiable in my view.

1358
02:20:57,030 --> 02:21:00,630
这个问题有两个方面  格瑞里先生  任何问题都是多方面的
-There are two sides to that question... -There are several sides...

1359
02:21:00,930 --> 02:21:03,430
可只有一面是正确的
...but only one right side, as with any question...

1360
02:21:03,630 --> 02:21:05,830
...只要问题涉及到滥用行政职权
...that involves the abuse of executive power.

1361
02:21:06,130 --> 02:21:08,330
无论如何  格瑞里先生
In any case, Mr. Greeley...

1362
02:21:08,630 --> 02:21:11,230
...我们应该庆幸情况没有恶化
...we can all be thankful that it wasn't any worse.

1363
02:21:11,530 --> 02:21:14,430
已经恶化了  先生  我都看见了  我不知道怎么办
It may be worse yet. I saw them. I don't know what to think.

1364
02:21:14,830 --> 02:21:17,930
你常挂在嘴边的是哪句话?特威德先生?
Now what is it that you are so fond of saying, Mr. Tweed?

1365
02:21:18,230 --> 02:21:20,530
格瑞里先生  那句话你不喜欢想起来了吗?
Mr. Greeley, you won't like this. But what is it?

1366
02:21:20,830 --> 02:21:21,830
我不记得了
I don't remember.

1367
02:21:22,030 --> 02:21:26,630
'你总是可以招募穷人的一半去杀掉另一半'
"You can always hire one half of the poor to kill the other half."

1368
02:21:37,030 --> 02:21:39,330
我来向你道别
I've come to say goodbye.

1369
02:21:39,530 --> 02:21:42,430
我已经订了去加利福尼亚的票
I've booked passage for California.

1370
02:21:45,030 --> 02:21:47,730
珍妮  给我一天时间我会和你一起走
Jenny, give me one more day, and I'll go with you.

1371
02:21:47,930 --> 02:21:50,130
到那时你已经死了
You'll be dead by then.

1372
02:21:50,830 --> 02:21:54,130
-那你要我怎么做?  -我不知道
-Well, what would you have me do? -I don't know.

1373
02:21:56,930 --> 02:22:00,530
-明天一切都会结束了  -不会的
-This will all be finished tomorrow. -No, it won't.

1374
02:22:02,330 --> 02:22:03,830
不
No.

1375
02:22:04,330 --> 02:22:07,230
这个地方要全部烧毁
This whole place is gonna burn anyway.

1376
02:22:15,430 --> 02:22:19,930
我听说穷人们在五分区正挨家挨户地
I've heard that the poor are going from door to door in the Five Points...

1377
02:22:20,330 --> 02:22:23,730
...要求那些希望继续闹事的人们
...asking those supporters who wish to see further riots...

1378
02:22:24,130 --> 02:22:27,030
...在窗口点燃一枝蜡烛
...to place a lighted candle in the window.

1379
02:22:27,630 --> 02:22:29,530
爱尔兰人  波兰人  德国人所有的人
Irish, Poles, Germans, all of them.

1380
02:22:30,530 --> 02:22:36,530
格瑞里先生  城市不是疯了  我预言今夜漆黑一片
Mr. Greeley, the city is not mad. I prophesy a very dark night.

1381
02:22:58,930 --> 02:23:02,630
今天谁都不要上班  我们要关闭工厂
Nobody goes to work today! We'll shut the factories down!

1382
02:23:02,930 --> 02:23:07,230
第二天太阳升起的时候  整个城市分成了两半
When the sun rose next, the city had split in half.

1383
02:23:07,530 --> 02:23:09,330
人们从纽约各处赶来
From all over New York they came:

1384
02:23:09,630 --> 02:23:12,330
铁场工人  工厂职员  清洁工人
Ironworkers, factory boys, street cleaners...

1385
02:23:12,530 --> 02:23:14,130
爱尔兰人  波兰人  德国人
...Irish, Polish, German...

1386
02:23:14,330 --> 02:23:17,030
从来没关心过奴隶制和联盟的人
...anyone who never cared about slavery or the Union...

1387
02:23:17,330 --> 02:23:19,730
所有没有钱逃避征兵的人
...anyone who couldn 't buy his way out.

1388
02:23:20,030 --> 02:23:22,930
他们高喊'让富人的孩子去送死吧'
"Let the sons of the rich go and die, " they cried.

1389
02:23:23,130 --> 02:23:26,030
'让穷人的孩子留在家中'
"Let the sons of the poor stay home."

1390
02:23:27,630 --> 02:23:29,630
此刻天摇地动
The earth was shaking now.

1391
02:23:29,930 --> 02:23:32,530
而我则着手于父亲的事业
But I was about my father's business.

1392
02:23:37,730 --> 02:23:39,830
一群第五大街的败类
A bunch of fifth Avenue scums!

1393
02:23:47,130 --> 02:23:51,430
万能的主啊  你就是我手中的匕首
Almighty Lord, you are the dagger in my hand.

1394
02:23:52,930 --> 02:23:55,130
在此复仇之日导引我的手
Guide my hand on this day of vengeance.

1395
02:23:55,430 --> 02:23:59,230
我们感谢上帝的仁慈
We give thanks to the Lord, for he is good.

1396
02:23:59,630 --> 02:24:03,730
有你在  敌人插翅难逃
With you, the swift cannot flee, nor the strong escape.

1397
02:24:04,130 --> 02:24:08,130
让我的剑饱饮鲜血直到不再干渴
Let my sword devour until its thirst is quenched with blood...

1398
02:24:08,530 --> 02:24:10,430
让我的敌人已长眠不起
...and my enemies sleep forever.

1399
02:24:10,730 --> 02:24:12,930
因为你是报应之主
For you are the Lord God of Retribution.

1400
02:24:13,230 --> 02:24:15,630
因为你是镇邪之主
For the Lord crushes the wicked.

1401
02:24:15,830 --> 02:24:18,330
因主充满慈悲
The Lord is merciful...

1402
02:24:19,030 --> 02:24:22,730
格瑞里先生他的慈爱永远长存
...and his love endures forever.

1403
02:24:23,430 --> 02:24:24,730
-阿门  -阿门
-Amen. -Amen.

1404
02:24:25,030 --> 02:24:26,130
阿门
Amen.

1405
02:24:32,230 --> 02:24:35,130
-快走  狗娘养的  -快出去
-Run away, you sons of bitches! -Come on out!

1406
02:24:37,730 --> 02:24:41,730
-上楼  让女眷到楼上去  -爸爸  爸爸
-Upstairs! Get the women upstairs! -Father! Father!

1407
02:24:45,730 --> 02:24:48,030
抓住这些畜生
Let's take the bastards!

1408
02:24:49,130 --> 02:24:53,030
18区  暴徒正在洗劫27街和第七大道住宅
From 18th Precinct: The mob are sacking houses, 27th Street and Seventh Ave.

1409
02:24:53,330 --> 02:24:54,630
我们已没有武力可派遣
We have no force to send.

1410
02:24:54,930 --> 02:24:58,030
16区  第八大道的所有商店都已关门
16th Precinct: All the stores are closing on Eighth Avenue...

1411
02:24:58,330 --> 02:25:00,230
因为害怕十七街的暴徒
...from fear of the mob in 17th Street.

1412
02:25:00,530 --> 02:25:02,930
看看你们有什么手段  胆小鬼
Show us what you got, you cowardly bastards!

1413
02:25:04,830 --> 02:25:07,830
第四区  闹事者袭击了有色人种公寓
From 4th: The rioters are robbing colored boarding houses...

1414
02:25:08,030 --> 02:25:10,430
...洗劫一空后放火烧楼  21区
...and setting them on fire. From 21st:

1415
02:25:11,930 --> 02:25:14,830
暴徒们冲入位于3大道的一家枪械店
The mob have just broken open gun store and are arming.

1416
02:25:19,530 --> 02:25:22,030
-抓住黑鬼  杀了他  杀了他
-Get the nigger! Kill him! -Tear Tammany down!

1417
02:25:22,230 --> 02:25:25,330
位于3大道的美国警署正在燃烧  警察束手无策
The marshal's office is burning down. The police is of no avail.

1418
02:25:25,630 --> 02:25:26,630
出来  特威德
Show yourself, Tweed!

1419
02:25:26,930 --> 02:25:28,530
两位有色人种濒临死亡
Two colored men brought in almost dead.

1420
02:25:30,530 --> 02:25:33,830
有50多位黑人需要救援  黑人四处被袭击
There are more Negroes who need help. They're being attacked all over.

1421
02:25:34,230 --> 02:25:35,930
那有个富家子弟  抓住他
Hey! There's a $300 man. Get him!

1422
02:25:36,230 --> 02:25:39,230
你老爸花钱让你不用参军  是吗?  他能帮我出这个钱吗?
Did your daddy buy you out of the Army? Can he buy me out too?

1423
02:25:40,730 --> 02:25:44,630
位于21街二大道的军火库有被暴徒袭击的危险
There's danger of mob attacking armory, corner 21st Street, Second Avenue.

1424
02:25:44,930 --> 02:25:47,030
里面约有500件武器
There is about 500 stand of arms in it.

1425
02:25:53,230 --> 02:25:56,130
线路断了  暴徒正在破坏所有的线路
The line is dead! They're trying to cut all the wires!

1426
02:25:59,530 --> 02:26:02,830
1区  暴徒们聚集在北河4码头  他们杀死了那里的黑人
From 1st: Riot at Pier 4, North River. They have killed Negroes.

1427
02:26:03,130 --> 02:26:06,030
一群人正准备摧毁整个港口
A crowd is here and are going to destroy this station.

1428
02:26:09,130 --> 02:26:11,230
抢她的包  抢她的包
Get her bag! Get her bag!

1429
02:26:13,430 --> 02:26:14,430
18区
From 18th Precinct:

1430
02:26:14,730 --> 02:26:19,230
暴徒袭击了军械库  大楼有着火的危险
The mob have attacked the armory. There is danger of firing the building.

1431
02:26:19,630 --> 02:26:22,030
所有三百名警察都已受伤或下落不明
All 300 police wounded or unaccounted for.

1432
02:26:22,330 --> 02:26:23,830
请寻找军队并派至...
Find the military and send them...

1433
02:26:23,930 --> 02:26:28,130
20街  派遣100个人驱散攻击市长住处的歹徒
From 20th: Send 100 men to disperse mob assailing Mayor Opdyke's house.

1434
02:26:28,530 --> 02:26:30,130
2大道33街的建筑物被暴徒焚烧
Building set on fire by the mob.

1435
02:26:33,130 --> 02:26:36,330
巴南姆博物馆正在起火  动物正在逃生
Barnum 's American Muzeum on fire. Animals are escaping.

1436
02:26:36,730 --> 02:26:39,030
走  走
Let go! Let go!

1437
02:26:39,730 --> 02:26:42,230
让这婊子别叫唤了  按住她
Hush the shickster! Hold her down!

1438
02:26:54,030 --> 02:26:57,930
'自由号'及'帕萨克号'停泊在华尔街附近
Gunboat Liberty and ironclad Passaic now lying off the foot of Wall Street.

1439
02:26:58,130 --> 02:27:00,030
他们已准备好向暴徒开火
They are ready to open fire on the mob.

1440
02:27:00,330 --> 02:27:02,630
-大批暴徒正前往5大道...
-Very large mob going to attack Tribune office.

1441
02:27:04,230 --> 02:27:06,830
16区  暴徒正前往火车站   我们已无人手
From 16th: Mob 's coming down to station. We have no men.

1442
02:27:07,030 --> 02:27:10,230
-18区-暴徒非常凶猛  -16区  军队已经抵达
-18th: The mob is very wild. -From 16th: 7th Regiment has arrived.

1443
02:27:10,530 --> 02:27:12,530
正从运河街赶往百老汇
Foot of Canal, they are on their way to Broadway.

1444
02:27:12,830 --> 02:27:14,030
拿开你的手
Take your hands off me!

1445
02:27:14,230 --> 02:27:16,130
暴徒大约有4500人
The mob is about 4500 strong.

1446
02:27:16,430 --> 02:27:19,430
他们要焚烧哈莱姆大桥  哈莱姆大桥已被点燃
They're going to burn down Harlem Bridge. It is to be torched.

1447
02:27:19,630 --> 02:27:22,530
-格瑞里先生  -鼠辈们占领了城市
-Mr. Greeley! - The rats have taken over the city!

1448
02:27:25,830 --> 02:27:29,430
21区  发生一起袭击有色人种事件
From 21st: There is an attack on the colored people in Second Avenue...

1449
02:27:29,730 --> 02:27:32,830
有一名暴徒前往有色人种孤儿院  派军队去保护孩子
Mob headed for the Colored Orphans Asylum. Protect the children!

1450
02:27:33,230 --> 02:27:34,830
7大道28街发生暴乱中央大街
Rioters on Seventh Avenue, 28th Street.

1451
02:27:36,330 --> 02:27:38,030
-他们刚杀了一名黑人  -抓住他
-They have killed a Negro. -Get him!

1452
02:27:38,330 --> 02:27:40,430
怎么处理犯人
What do we do with captured prisoners?

1453
02:27:40,730 --> 02:27:43,530
犯人?  别管犯人了  暴徒不会对付犯人
Prisoners? Don't take any. The mob isn't taking prisoners!

1454
02:27:43,830 --> 02:27:47,130
平息暴乱前别抓犯人
Don't take a prisoner in until you've put the mob down!

1455
02:27:54,530 --> 02:27:58,330
军队在38街  暴徒不肯散去
Soldiers now on 38th Street. The mob will not disperse.

1456
02:27:58,730 --> 02:28:01,130
请你快下命令  请你快下命令
What are your orders? What are your orders?

1457
02:28:15,930 --> 02:28:20,730
-不征兵  不征兵  -让他们知道我们对征兵的看法
-No draft! No draft! -Show them what we think of their draft!

1458
02:28:27,730 --> 02:28:29,230
-站在一起  -好的
-Stick together! -All right.

1459
02:28:33,430 --> 02:28:35,430
立定!
Troop, halt!

1460
02:28:36,330 --> 02:28:38,730
出枪!
Present arms!

1461
02:28:44,630 --> 02:28:46,130
我依约前来  瓦伦
On your order, Vallon.

1462
02:28:48,430 --> 02:28:50,230
坚持 坚持住
Hold fast, there. Hold fast, there.

1463
02:28:50,330 --> 02:28:53,130
我命令你们疏散
I order you to disperse!

1464
02:28:56,530 --> 02:28:58,030
开枪
Fire!

1465
02:29:33,530 --> 02:29:35,730
右舷开火
Fire starboard!

1466
02:29:48,930 --> 02:29:51,630
右舷猛攻  开火!
Starboard battery, fire!

1467
02:30:01,330 --> 02:30:02,930
快走
Come on, let's go!

1468
02:30:09,430 --> 02:30:11,430
枪往他们头上打
Fire over their heads!

1469
02:30:12,330 --> 02:30:14,430
把他们赶进广场
Drive them into the square!

1470
02:30:17,330 --> 02:30:19,030
比尔
Bill!

1471
02:30:26,730 --> 02:30:28,030
开火
Fire!

1472
02:30:28,730 --> 02:30:30,230
前进
Advance!

1473
02:30:31,030 --> 02:30:32,830
比尔
Bill!

1474
02:30:36,030 --> 02:30:37,330
我走不动了
I can't walk!

1475
02:30:39,230 --> 02:30:40,630
起来
Get up!

1476
02:31:44,330 --> 02:31:45,630
开火
Fire!

1477
02:32:14,030 --> 02:32:17,730
-畜生  -商!  商!  别过去
-Bastards! -Shang! Shang, hold off!

1478
02:32:50,230 --> 02:32:52,230
感谢上帝
Thank God.

1479
02:32:53,330 --> 02:32:56,030
我死得象个真正的美国人
I die a true American.

1480
02:34:58,130 --> 02:35:00,530
明天早上  我们的人全得到码头去
Tomorrow morning, get our people down to the docks.

1481
02:35:01,830 --> 02:35:06,130
我要每个下船的人们都能拿到热汤和面包
I want every man and woman coming off the boats given hot soup and bread.

1482
02:35:10,730 --> 02:35:14,130
今晚我们在这里埋掉不少选票
We're burying a lot of votes down here tonight.

1483
02:35:31,830 --> 02:35:36,430
最后  人们在尸体上点燃蜡烛这样他们的朋友
In the end, they put candles on the bodies so 's their friends...

1484
02:35:36,830 --> 02:35:40,830
...如果他们有的话  在黑暗中能认出他们来
...if they had any, could know them in the dark.

1485
02:35:42,230 --> 02:35:45,530
这是市府免费提供的
The city did this free of charge.

1486
02:35:46,730 --> 02:35:52,530
商  吉米.斯波尔斯  地狱猫  麦格罗恩  还有更多人
Shang, Jimmy Spoils, Hell-Cat, McGloin and more.

1487
02:35:54,230 --> 02:35:58,530
敌或友  现在已没有了区别
Friend or foe, it didn 't make no difference now.

1488
02:36:18,230 --> 02:36:24,030
经过了四个昼夜  暴动终于得以平息
It was four days and nights before the worst of the mob was finally put down.

1489
02:36:25,330 --> 02:36:27,830
期间多少纽约人命丧黄泉永远不可得知
We never knew how many New Yorkers died that week...

1490
02:36:28,130 --> 02:36:30,830
...在城市重获新生之前
...before the city was finally delivered.

1491
02:36:32,330 --> 02:36:37,230
父亲说我们都诞于苦难与鲜血之中
My father told me we was all born of blood and tribulation.

1492
02:36:38,530 --> 02:36:42,630
我们伟大的城市也是如此
And so then too was our great city.

1493
02:36:45,730 --> 02:36:50,230
那些激情燃烧的岁月里的生死恩怨
But for those of us what lived and died in them furious days...

1494
02:36:50,630 --> 02:36:55,830
...正如我们所熟悉的一切终成过眼云烟
...it was like everything we knew was mightily swept away.

1495
02:36:56,930 --> 02:36:59,930
重建城市的人们  不管付出多少血泪
And no matter what they did to build the city up again...

1496
02:37:02,330 --> 02:37:04,830
...随着时光流逝...
...for the rest of time...

1497
02:37:05,830 --> 02:37:10,030
...终如春梦一般  了却无痕
...it would be like no one even knew we was ever here.

